lead_paragraph: Lindsay Allen recorded her first career triple-double and Brianna Turner scored 24 points to help No. 2 Notre Dame beat Chattanooga 79-58 on Tuesday night for its 15th consecutive road victory.

headline.print_headline: Allen Helps No. 2 Notre Dame Women Defeat Chattanooga 79-58
